<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>How We Work Layout</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            brandBrown: '#5c3d38',
            brandGold: '#f7cc55',
            brandDarkBg: '#4a312e',
            textGray: '#555555',
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="font-sans text-gray-800 bg-[#fbfbf9]">

  <section class="relative bg-cover bg-center h-[450px] flex items-end pb-12" style="background-image: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 w-full text-white">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">How We Work</h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-200">
        Our programs empower children and youth with intellectual disabilities to reach their full potential through balanced education, vocational training, inclusive community building, and advocacy for lasting change.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brandBrown mb-8">Learn More About Our Programs</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <a href="#education" class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded text-brandBrown font-medium hover:bg-brandGold hover:text-brandBrown transition">
          <span>Education Programs</span> <span>&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#vocational" class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded text-brandBrown font-medium hover:bg-brandGold hover:text-brandBrown transition">
          <span>Vocational Training</span> <span>&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#teacher" class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded text-brandBrown font-medium hover:bg-brandGold hover:text-brandBrown transition">
          <span>Teacher Training</span> <span>&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#advocacy" class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded text-brandBrown font-medium hover:bg-brandGold hover:text-brandBrown transition">
          <span>Advocacy & Community</span> <span>&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="education" class="py-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brandBrown uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Education Programs</h2>
      <h3 class="text-sky-600 font-semibold mb-6">Empowering Bright Minds to Embrace Life's Opportunities</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-textGray leading-relaxed text-sm">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brandBrown mb-1">Specialized Education</h4>
          <p>At our specialized centers, we deliver tailored education programs engineered to nurture individual developmental goals. We focus on basic academic foundation concepts alongside daily life skill development to prepare students for greater future self-reliance.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brandBrown mb-1">Integrated Classrooms</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Tailored class spaces designed to match learning levels.</li>
            <li>Access to specialized therapists for behavioral and sensory support.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brandBrown mb-1">Inclusive Classrooms</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Active integration in mainstream local school systems.</li>
            <li>Collaborations with community teachers for regular progress tracking.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full h-80 md:h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1427504494785-3a9ca7044f45?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Education Program" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-gray-200 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

  <section id="vocational" class="py-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <div class="relative w-full h-80 md:h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md order-2 md:order-1">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513258496099-48168024addd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Vocational Training" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 max-w-xs">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brandBrown uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1">Our Location</span>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Tuol Kork Primary School, Phnom Penh</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brandBrown uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Vocational Training & Job Placement</h2>
      <h3 class="text-red-500 font-semibold mb-6">Building Life-Long Skills</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-textGray leading-relaxed text-sm">
        <p>This initiative bridges the gap between educational learning and sustainable employment. We focus on practical, hands-on trades that match market demands, opening up doors to independent livelihoods.</p>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brandBrown mb-2">What Students Learn</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Handicrafts and hospitality workflows</li>
            <li>Basic computer and administration tasks</li>
            <li>Interpersonal relationship and customer service skills</li>
            <li>Managing personal finances through practical games</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-gray-200 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

  <section id="teacher" class="py-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brandBrown uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Teacher Training</h2>
      <h3 class="text-sky-600 font-semibold mb-6">Building Teacher Capacity for Inclusive Education</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-textGray leading-relaxed text-sm">
        <p>We actively equip educators with progressive tools to confidently manage special needs classrooms, creating a scalable, supportive network throughout schools nationwide.</p>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brandBrown mb-2">What We Do:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Train teachers to screen students for early intervention.</li>
            <li>Host monthly sharing circles to brainstorm collective solutions.</li>
            <li>Provide continuous resources for adapted curriculum mapping.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full h-80 md:h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544535830-9dff9a014bb5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Teacher Training" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="advocacy" class="py-16 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brandBrown uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Advocacy and Community Building</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-textGray text-sm leading-relaxed mb-12">
        We work closely with local authorities and parents to integrate inclusive programs into the public system. Together, we target stigmas around intellectual disabilities, creating an environment focused on ability and contribution.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472653425546-57688557e94e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Event Run" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="py-4 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 font-medium text-sm text-brandBrown">
            Event Run with Sól
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524178232363-1fb2b075b655?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Parent Training" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="py-4 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 font-medium text-sm text-brandBrown">
            Parent's Training
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515187029135-18ee286d815b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Employment Forum" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="py-4 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 font-medium text-sm text-brandBrown">
            Participation in Employment National Forum
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-brandDarkBg text-gray-300 text-xs py-12 border-t-4 border-brandGold">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
      <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
        <div class="font-bold text-white text-base mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-brandGold text-xl">🐰</span> The Rabbit School
        </div>
        <button class="mt-2 bg-brandGold text-brandDarkBg font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-400 transition flex items-center gap-1">
          Donate <span class="text-sm">&rarr;</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-3">Our Program</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Education Program</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Vocational Training</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Teacher Training</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Advocacy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-3">About Us</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Our Story</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Where We Work</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Our Partners</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-3">News</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Press Corner</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Publications</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Videos</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h5 class="text-white font-bold mb-3">Contact</h5>
        <p class="mb-2">📍 Tuol Kork Primary School, Phnom Penh</p>
        <p class="mb-2">📞 +855 12 345 678</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mt-12 pt-4 border-t border-gray-700 text-center text-gray-400 text-[10px]">
      © 2026 The Rabbit School. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>